Home page
- Will show all your armies similar to how GW app
  shows them.
- From here, you can delete or duplicate rosters

Top right will be a "Add new wargame" button
- This will let you download a new repository
  (ex. Warhammer 40k, some other wargame, etc.)

Bottom right will be a "New roster" sign
- This will let you create a new roster
- It opens a page titled "What game"

Picking the game system displays all the .json files
available in that repo (i.e. all the factions)

Picking a faction displays all the detachments available
to that faction

